{"tid":2026350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曉麗苑 法團開會又玩野","createTime":"2020-05-21T01:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T14:30:57.000Z","uid":267365,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ad47103d80e5807f2e375a964bfdbb769a33c252","tid":2026350,"uid":267365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:44:01.000Z","msg":"早前曉麗苑法團主席蘇麗珍(貴洲政協, 創建力量副主席), 4月頭收到10%業主要求開會重選法團委員.她居然用疫情限聚令再三推諉延遲召開業主特別大會. 居然噚晚自己又出通告, 下星期四28/5 晚召開法團常務會議. <br />\n佢開就得, 就冇犯限聚令, 業主按法例要求佢又唔聽. 龍門任佢搬.<br />\n最搞笑個會議議程連分項總共41項討論. 每項傾十分鐘, 都要6.8個鐘. 成班退休長者委員真係登佢地辛苦.<br />\n平時唔做野, 到宜家俾人踢走就一次過想做返.......<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5KLd8Cm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5KLd8Cm.jpg&h=223ee7a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyqUS33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyqUS33.jpg&h=7a6b58ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa337985091130d938fdae0d0afb1cb013671a59","tid":2026350,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:46:28.000Z","msg":"魔鬼在細節<br />\n總共只可以俾5個業主出席?"},{"pid":"e4d634c397809fe6059bc40aa116b38d9d3ae8fd","tid":2026350,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa337985091130d938fdae0d0afb1cb013671a59","tid":2026350,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:46:28.000Z","msg":"魔鬼在細節<br />\n總共只可以俾5個業主出席?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:54:54.000Z","msg":"精選5個&quot;業主&quot;出黎開會<br />\n睇黎又要有一番激烈衝突<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd62705cd64864eb1e2b98b12fdf10b78b39a15","tid":2026350,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:43:51.000Z","msg":"推呢個post<br />\n曉麗苑頻爆渠無水沖涼　關注組批法團不作為　集齊業主簽名求推翻<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2026550\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2026550</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7c4a454c343ea0254b1263452169bdb7891b4581","tid"